text: St. Francis College - Guihulngan (also known as SFC-G) is a private educational institution located in Bateria, Guihulngan, Negros Oriental, Philippines. Inspired by the Charism of St. Francis of Assisi, three Franciscan friars including Brother Norbert Binder founded and managed the school. ==References== Category:Universities and colleges in Negros Oriental
title: St. Francis College Guihulngan
